column44: The dataset provides yearly retention and six-year graduation outcomes for full-time, first-time students from 2013 to 2023. It is broken down by gender and race/ethnicity, including under-represented minorities, and shows both the size of the original cohorts and their progression over time. The data highlights trends in retention from the first to second year and long-term graduation rates across different demographic groups
